{"TopicId":131747,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"The Need for Speed: Speed record","CreatedByName":"fortraan","CreatedById":157761,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T18:44:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"fortraan","CreatedById":157761,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T18:44:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe name is pretty self explanatory: just make something that goes as fast as possible!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMods are allowed!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe idea is to see the limits of KSP, and just how fast you can go without destroying the craft, game, etc. HyperEdit, FTL drive, and the like are allowed to get you to where you will test your design. Other than that, nearly everything is fair game!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Windspren","CreatedById":134441,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T04:55:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan I fire up my old K-Drive? I got to over 200c with that thing (200 times the speed of light)!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"superstrijder15","CreatedById":155985,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T09:55:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo turn on infinite fuel, send out probe with engine, wait forever?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Evanitis","CreatedById":145424,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T09:57:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222401841\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131747\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455098140\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155985\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022superstrijder15\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, superstrijder15 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo turn on infinite fuel, send out probe with engine, wait forever?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut the forever you wait, the more score you get.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fortraan","CreatedById":157761,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T13:58:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222401685\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131747\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455080124\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022134441\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laythe Dweller\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Laythe Dweller said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan I fire up my old K-Drive? I got to over 200c with that thing (200 times the speed of light)!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike I said, this challenge i to see just how fast you can have something move before the game can\u0027t handle it. So, yes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222401841\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131747\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455098140\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155985\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022superstrijder15\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, superstrijder15 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo turn on infinite fuel, send out probe with engine, wait forever?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, that\u0027s one way to do it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fortraan","CreatedById":157761,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T16:10:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI realized that I need to post my attempt. But, my parents won\u0027t let me use my computer\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I can describe what I will most likely do: A Mk. 2 that has shorter Mk. 2 fuel tanks on either side on the back. For engines, 3 \u0022Advanced turbo ramjets\u0022 (I believe they are either from Quiztech Aero or OPT). I will have to carry oxygen with me for space testing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"superstrijder15","CreatedById":155985,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T18:30:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just got 20 km/s in 5 min, main point is its boring\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}